{"chapters": {"ch01-o-circulo-dourado": ["<div class=\"slide cover\"><div class=\"wordmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span><span class=\"name\">Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"kicker\">COMO GRANDES LÍDERES INSPIRAM A AGIR</div><h1><span class=\"lt\">COMECE PELO</span> <span class=\"bd\">PORQUÊ</span></h1><div class=\"author\">por Simon Sinek</div><div class=\"hook\"><span class=\"num\">4</span><span class=\"lbl\">ideias<br>que <span>ficam</span></span></div><div class=\"swipe\"><span>arrasta</span><span class=\"arrow\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M12 32h36M34 18l16 14-16 14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">01</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>01</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"22\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"12\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"2.5\" fill=\"currentColor\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">Os Três Anéis</div><div class=\"card-body\"><strong>O QUÊ</strong>: o produto/serviço — todos sabem o seu. <strong>COMO</strong>: os diferenciais e valores. <strong>PORQUÊ</strong>: a causa/crença pela qual você existe — <em>nunca</em> 'lucrar' (lucro é resultado).</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Como aplicar:</strong> escreva seu Porquê em uma frase. Se não cabe numa frase clara, ele ainda não está definido.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">02</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>02</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 32a6 6 0 1 1 6 6 12 12 0 1 1-12-12 18 18 0 1 1 18 18\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">De Dentro para Fora</div><div class=\"card-body\">O discurso que inspira começa pela crença e termina no produto. O mesmo produto, na ordem certa, deixa de ser 'compre' e passa a ser desejo. <strong>Só muda a ordem</strong> — e muda tudo.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Modelo mental:</strong> pessoas não compram o que você faz; compram <em>por que</em> você faz.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept warn\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">03</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>03</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 56V34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 34L16 14M32 34l16-20\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><circle cx=\"16\" cy=\"12\" r=\"4\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><circle cx=\"48\" cy=\"12\" r=\"4\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">Manipular × Inspirar</div><div class=\"card-body\">As 6 manipulações: <strong>preço, promoções, medo, aspiração, pressão dos pares, novidade</strong>. Funcionam, mas viciam e não criam lealdade. A inspiração nasce do Porquê.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 8l20 8v13c0 14-9 23-20 27-11-4-20-13-20-27V16z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Para refletir:</strong> guerra de preço ensina o cliente a comprar só por preço — insustentável.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">04</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>04</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">O Exemplo Apple</div><div class=\"card-body\">'Em tudo que fazemos, desafiamos o status quo (Porquê). Fazemos isso com produtos lindos e simples (Como). E acontece que fazemos ótimos computadores (O Quê).' A mesma empresa — agora você quer comprar.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Como aplicar:</strong> teste seu pitch — ele abre pela crença ou pelas características?</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide cta\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"bottom:150px;right:40px;font-size:300px\">+</div><div class=\"big\">Gostou?<br><span class=\"lt\">tem mais.</span></div><div class=\"rows\"><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M14 12h36v40H14z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M14 24h36M14 38h36M24 12v12M40 24v14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>O livro inteiro em 1 página: cheat sheet + PDF no <strong>acervo</strong> &mdash; link na bio.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"22\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><path d=\"M27 23l16 9-16 9z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Prefere assistir? Resumo de ~5 min no <strong>YouTube</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Um grande livro destilado por semana. <strong>Siga @minutoreal1701</strong>.</p></div></div><div class=\"save\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M18 10h28v44L32 44 18 54z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>Salve para revisar</div><div class=\"handle\">@minutoreal1701</div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i></div></div>"], "ch02-biologia-clareza-confianca": ["<div class=\"slide cover\"><div class=\"wordmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span><span class=\"name\">Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"kicker\">COMO GRANDES LÍDERES INSPIRAM A AGIR</div><h1><span class=\"lt\">COMECE PELO</span> <span class=\"bd\">PORQUÊ</span></h1><div class=\"author\">por Simon Sinek</div><div class=\"hook\"><span class=\"num\">3</span><span class=\"lbl\">ideias<br>que <span>ficam</span></span></div><div class=\"swipe\"><span>arrasta</span><span class=\"arrow\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M12 32h36M34 18l16 14-16 14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept warn\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">01</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>01</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>03</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 32a6 6 0 1 1 6 6 12 12 0 1 1-12-12 18 18 0 1 1 18 18\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">O Cérebro Decide no Límbico</div><div class=\"card-body\">O <strong>neocórtex</strong> (O Quê) entende fatos e linguagem, mas não decide. O <strong>sistema límbico</strong> (Porquê/Como) governa sentimento, confiança e a decisão — e <em>não tem linguagem</em>. Daí o 'sinto que está certo'.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 8l20 8v13c0 14-9 23-20 27-11-4-20-13-20-27V16z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Modelo mental:</strong> mais dados não vencem a falta de Porquê — a decisão é do coração.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">02</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>02</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>03</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M10 52h12V40h12V28h12V16h8\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">Clareza · Disciplina · Consistência</div><div class=\"card-body\"><strong>Clareza</strong> do Porquê (saber em palavras), <strong>disciplina</strong> do Como (valores viram <em>verbos</em>) e <strong>consistência</strong> do O Quê (tudo prova o Porquê). É o que gera autenticidade.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Como aplicar:</strong> transforme cada valor em verbo — 'integridade' → 'fazer o certo mesmo quando custa'.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">03</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>03</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>03</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M26 38l12-12\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><path d=\"M22 32l-6 6a8 8 0 0 0 11 11l6-6\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><path d=\"M42 32l6-6a8 8 0 0 0-11-11l-6 6\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">Confiança = Crença Compartilhada</div><div class=\"card-body\">Confiança não se ordena: surge quando os valores batem. Por isso, <strong>contrate por atitude/crença, treine a habilidade</strong> (Herb Kelleher, Southwest). Quem acredita entrega muito além do salário.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Modelo mental:</strong> primeiro pergunte 'ele acredita no que acreditamos?', depois olhe o currículo.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide cta\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"bottom:150px;right:40px;font-size:300px\">+</div><div class=\"big\">Gostou?<br><span class=\"lt\">tem mais.</span></div><div class=\"rows\"><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M14 12h36v40H14z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M14 24h36M14 38h36M24 12v12M40 24v14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>O livro inteiro em 1 página: cheat sheet + PDF no <strong>acervo</strong> &mdash; link na bio.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"22\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><path d=\"M27 23l16 9-16 9z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Prefere assistir? Resumo de ~5 min no <strong>YouTube</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Um grande livro destilado por semana. <strong>Siga @minutoreal1701</strong>.</p></div></div><div class=\"save\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M18 10h28v44L32 44 18 54z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>Salve para revisar</div><div class=\"handle\">@minutoreal1701</div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i></div></div>"], "ch03-difusao-e-teste-do-aipo": ["<div class=\"slide cover\"><div class=\"wordmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span><span class=\"name\">Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"kicker\">COMO GRANDES LÍDERES INSPIRAM A AGIR</div><h1><span class=\"lt\">COMECE PELO</span> <span class=\"bd\">PORQUÊ</span></h1><div class=\"author\">por Simon Sinek</div><div class=\"hook\"><span class=\"num\">4</span><span class=\"lbl\">ideias<br>que <span>ficam</span></span></div><div class=\"swipe\"><span>arrasta</span><span class=\"arrow\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M12 32h36M34 18l16 14-16 14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">01</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>01</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M6 50l16-30 10 16 8-12 18 26z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">A Lei da Difusão da Inovação</div><div class=\"card-body\">Curva em sino: inovadores (2,5%), <strong>adotantes iniciais (13,5%)</strong>, maioria inicial (34%), maioria tardia (34%), retardatários (16%). Os primeiros 16% compram o seu <strong>Porquê</strong>.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Como aplicar:</strong> mire os que já creem (esquerda da curva); não tente convencer a maioria primeiro.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept warn\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">02</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>02</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 56s16-14 16-28a16 16 0 0 0-32 0c0 14 16 28 16 28z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"28\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">O Ponto de Inflexão</div><div class=\"card-body\">Não dá para alcançar o mercado de massa direto. Só após <strong>~15-18% de penetração</strong> a maioria segue. A TiVo falhou por comunicar <em>recursos</em> (O Quê), não crença (Porquê).</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 8l20 8v13c0 14-9 23-20 27-11-4-20-13-20-27V16z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Modelo mental:</strong> a maioria 'pega' a ideia de quem confia, não da propaganda.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">03</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>03</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M48 14C28 14 14 28 14 48c20 0 34-14 34-34z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M22 42L42 22\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">O Teste do Aipo</div><div class=\"card-body\">Diante de várias 'boas ideias' ou conselhos, aceite <strong>só o que prova o seu Porquê</strong> e rejeite o resto, por lucrativo que pareça. Quem olha seu 'carrinho' lê sua crença só pela coerência.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Como aplicar:</strong> 'boa ideia' não basta — tem de ser <em>coerente</em> com a crença.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">04</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>04</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M10 14h44v28H30l-12 10v-10H10z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M20 24h24M20 32h16\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">Tenho um Sonho</div><div class=\"card-body\">Martin Luther King não disse 'tenho um plano' (O Quê), e sim '<strong>tenho um sonho</strong>' (Porquê). 250 mil foram por elas mesmas — pela própria crença. Símbolos só valem quando representam um Porquê.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Modelo mental:</strong> dê às pessoas algo em que crer; elas espalham a mensagem como sua.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide cta\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"bottom:150px;right:40px;font-size:300px\">+</div><div class=\"big\">Gostou?<br><span class=\"lt\">tem mais.</span></div><div class=\"rows\"><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M14 12h36v40H14z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M14 24h36M14 38h36M24 12v12M40 24v14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>O livro inteiro em 1 página: cheat sheet + PDF no <strong>acervo</strong> &mdash; link na bio.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"22\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><path d=\"M27 23l16 9-16 9z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Prefere assistir? Resumo de ~5 min no <strong>YouTube</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Um grande livro destilado por semana. <strong>Siga @minutoreal1701</strong>.</p></div></div><div class=\"save\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M18 10h28v44L32 44 18 54z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>Salve para revisar</div><div class=\"handle\">@minutoreal1701</div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i></div></div>"], "ch04-a-cisao-e-a-sucessao": ["<div class=\"slide cover\"><div class=\"wordmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span><span class=\"name\">Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"kicker\">COMO GRANDES LÍDERES INSPIRAM A AGIR</div><h1><span class=\"lt\">COMECE PELO</span> <span class=\"bd\">PORQUÊ</span></h1><div class=\"author\">por Simon Sinek</div><div class=\"hook\"><span class=\"num\">4</span><span class=\"lbl\">ideias<br>que <span>ficam</span></span></div><div class=\"swipe\"><span>arrasta</span><span class=\"arrow\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M12 32h36M34 18l16 14-16 14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept warn\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">01</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>01</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M10 32h16M38 32h16\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><path d=\"M22 24l-6 8 6 8M42 24l6 8-6 8\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">A Cisão do Porquê</div><div class=\"card-body\">Quando o sucesso escala, o foco migra do Porquê para o O Quê (métricas, preço). A crença se dilui e a manipulação volta. Distinga <strong>sucesso</strong> (atingir o O Quê) de <strong>realização</strong> (viver o Porquê).</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 8l20 8v13c0 14-9 23-20 27-11-4-20-13-20-27V16z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Modelo mental:</strong> faça o check-up — 'ainda sabemos por que existimos?'</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">02</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>02</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"20\" r=\"10\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><path d=\"M14 52c0-10 8-18 18-18s18 8 18 18\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">O Desafio da Sucessão</div><div class=\"card-body\">A Cisão se aprofunda quando o fundador sai: herdeiros recebem o negócio (O Quê), mas não a crença (Porquê). Sem ela, recorrem à manipulação e a cultura esfria (Walmart pós-Sam Walton).</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Como aplicar:</strong> forme sucessores como guardiães do Porquê, não só gestores do O Quê.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">03</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>03</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"22\" cy=\"22\" r=\"12\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><path d=\"M30 30l22 22M44 44l6-6M38 50l6-6\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">Descobrir o Porquê</div><div class=\"card-body\">O Porquê <strong>não se inventa, se descobre</strong> — olhando para trás, para a história e os valores que te formaram. Um Porquê de marketing soa falso e não passa no Teste do Aipo.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Para refletir:</strong> 'o que sempre me moveu, mesmo sem recompensa?' — o padrão recorrente é o Porquê.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">04</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>04</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">A Nova Competição</div><div class=\"card-body\">Quem vive o Porquê <strong>compete contra si mesmo</strong>, não contra o rival. Os irmãos Wright voaram por uma causa; Langley, com mais verba e fama (O Quê), desistiu quando perdeu o ineditismo.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Modelo mental:</strong> crença vence recurso — o Porquê sustenta quando dinheiro e fama acabam.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide cta\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"bottom:150px;right:40px;font-size:300px\">+</div><div class=\"big\">Gostou?<br><span class=\"lt\">tem mais.</span></div><div class=\"rows\"><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M14 12h36v40H14z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M14 24h36M14 38h36M24 12v12M40 24v14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>O livro inteiro em 1 página: cheat sheet + PDF no <strong>acervo</strong> &mdash; link na bio.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"22\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><path d=\"M27 23l16 9-16 9z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Prefere assistir? Resumo de ~5 min no <strong>YouTube</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Um grande livro destilado por semana. <strong>Siga @minutoreal1701</strong>.</p></div></div><div class=\"save\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M18 10h28v44L32 44 18 54z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>Salve para revisar</div><div class=\"handle\">@minutoreal1701</div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i></div></div>"]}}